frames.caption: A ballerina gracefully balances on the nose of a breaching orca amidst an icy seascape. The dancer is poised in an elegant arabesque, her white tutu contrasting with the orca's sleek black and white body. Icebergs and snow-covered mountains form a dramatic backdrop, enhancing the surreal beauty of the scene.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantastical moment where a ballerina performs atop a breaching orca in an icy, oceanic setting. The juxtaposition of the delicate dancer and the powerful marine mammal creates a striking visual contrast.
